<chapter condition="TITLE=General;" role="TOPIC">
    <title>General</title>

    <section role="ITEM">
      <title>Operations</title>

      <informaltable role="TEXT">
        <tgroup cols="3">
          <colspec colname="c1" colwidth="1.0*" />

          <colspec colname="c2" colwidth="2.0*" />

          <colspec colname="c3" colwidth="8.0*" />

          <thead>
            <row>
              <entry nameend="c2" namest="c1" valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Operation</para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">Description</para></entry>
            </row>
          </thead>

          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                  <imageobject>
                    <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_save.gif" role="ICON_SAVE"  width="10mm"/>
                  </imageobject>
                </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <guiicon moreinfo="none">Save</guiicon> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The transaction details entered will be saved as draft (or uncontrolled) which means that the Letter of Credit initiation will remain as a pending record without being sent to the issuing bank for now. No control on the mandatory fields is performed at this stage.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                  <imageobject>
                    <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_submit.gif" role="ICON_SUBMIT"  width="10mm"/>
                  </imageobject>
                </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <guiicon moreinfo="none">Submit</guiicon> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The user chooses this action when all the requested (and mandatory) details of the transaction have been entered and the resulting file is ready for submission to the issuing bank. </para> <para role="TEXT">Depending on the jurisdiction profile of the user (and in particular the amount he is authorised to validate without an additional signature), the transaction record will whether remain within the client workspace as unsigned or be sent to the bank's Trade Services back-office.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                  <imageobject>
                    <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_preview.gif" role="ICON_PREVIEW"  width="10mm"/>
                  </imageobject>
                </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <guiicon moreinfo="none">Preview</guiicon> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">This action is available in non-editable mode only (review of an unsigned record). It opens a new popup window with the details of the unsigned record and hence provides a simple way to print its content.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                  <imageobject>
                     <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_template.gif" role="ICON_TEMPLATE" width="10mm"/>
                  </imageobject>
                </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <guiicon moreinfo="none">Template</guiicon> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">This operation triggers a save of the transaction details entered in the Letter of Credit form into a template whose reference name is given in the <guilabel moreinfo="none">Template Id</guilabel> field which is therefore mandatory. If a template already bears this identifier, it is overridden by the current transaction details. </para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                  <imageobject>
                    <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_cancel.gif" role="ICON_CANCEL"  width="10mm"/>
                  </imageobject>
                </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <guiicon moreinfo="none">Cancel</guiicon> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">By choosing this operation, the user will leave the current page and will be brought back to the Letter of Credit general menu.</para></entry>
            </row>

            <row>
              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                  <imageobject>
                    <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_help.gif" role="ICON_HELP"  width="10mm"/>
                  </imageobject>
                </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="middle"><para role="TEXT"> <guiicon moreinfo="none">Help</guiicon> </para></entry>

              <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The user chooses this operation to open a popup window displaying the online help pages.</para></entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </informaltable>
    </section>
  </chapter>